 every month, until you cancel or adjust the number of member seats on your account. Sales tax may apply. All prices are in USD.",students:"You will be billed {planPrice} every month, until you cancel or adjust the number of student seats on your account. Sales tax may apply. All prices are in USD."}},subscriptionChanges:"If the rate for your subscription changes, we will notify you of the new amount at least 30 days in advance of the date of your next payment.",upgradeMessage:"Because your new plan is more expensive, we will bill you now for the price difference for the days remaining in your current monthly period.",downgradeMessage:"Because your new plan is less expensive, we will credit your account for the price difference for the days remaining in your current monthly period."},submit:{start:"Start My {name} Plan",switch:"Switch to {name} Plan"},vat:{finePrint:"By entering a VAT ID, you are agreeing to “reverse charge” for purposes of value-added tax (“VAT”) and/or goods and services tax (“GST”), as applicable. This means you are responsible for calculating and paying any applicable VAT or GST due with respect to purchases from us directly to the appropriate tax authority and reporting such amounts as part of your VAT and/or GST return(s), as applicable.",guidance:"Your VAT ID should begin with its applicable country code (e.g. in the United Kingdom, GB123456789)",vatId:"VAT ID"},errors:{required:"required",creditCardNumber:"Please enter a valid credit card number",expiry:"Please enter a valid expiration date",CVC:"Please enter a valid CVC code",cardDeclined:"Your card was declined",default:"There was an issue with your card",vatIdFormat:"VAT ID must begin with a two-letter country code"}},confirmation:{account:"account overview page",accountOverview:"account management pages",howTo:{alt:"How to navigate to Account Overview",title:"how to"},individual:{accountManagement:"To view and manage your account, you can go to your {overviewLink} at any time.",howTo:"Cl